classes.name: Intermediate layer bendpoint
classes.description: Element that allows to connect elements with relationclasses indirectly
classes.geometry: async function vizRep(gc) { await gc.graphic_sphere(0.05, 10, 10, 'black'); let icon = 'data:image/svg+xml;base64,'; }

classes.name: Device with 1 communication port
classes.description: A device of an IT infrastructure
classes.geometry: async function vizRep(gc){ await gc.setVariable('name', await gc.dynval('7d3c4c5e-68e5-4b6a-96be-2f3f34ad392a', await gc.get_current_class_instance_uuid()), false); await gc.setVariable('x_rel', -0.4, true); await gc.setVariable('y_rel', 0.1, true); await gc.setVariable('z_rel', -0.05, true); let map= 'data:image/svg+xml;base64,'; let icon = 'data:image/svg+xml;base64,'; await gc.graphic_cube(1, 0.8, 0.02, 'lightgrey', map); await gc.graphic_text(await gc.getVariableValue('x_rel'), await gc.getVariableValue('y_rel'), await gc.getVariableValue('z_rel'), 0.15, 'black', await gc.getVariableValue('name'), 'x_rel', 'y_rel', 'z_rel'); let portPower = await gc.getMetaPort('01a7181a-c1b7-4c51-aac9-09165043a429');  await gc.spec_port( await portPower(await gc.getNewGC()), 0,0.32,0.01); let portCommunication = await gc.getMetaPort('06f3ea47-92b6-479a-ba1f-ec9cc72fabac');  await gc.spec_port( await portCommunication(await gc.getNewGC()), 0.42,0,0.01); }
